title: ICPC Azerbaijan Qualification 2024
organization: ICPC Foundation / Azerbaijan Higher Education Institutions
description: Competed in the Azerbaijan Qualification round of the International Collegiate Programming Contest (ICPC), the premier global competitive programming competition. Ranked 67th overall in a highly competitive field of university-level problem solvers. Awarded the 'High Achievement' medal for exceptional performance in solving complex algorithmic challenges under strict time constraints. Demonstrated mastery in advanced data structures, graph theory, and dynamic programming using C++.
